  7. How long we hold your information for</h4>
</div>
<div id="78720" class="collapse m-b-24 clearfix" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="question-78720">
  <p>We'll retain information for no longer than is necessary and this will mean that we'll continue to hold some information for a period of time after our relationship has ended. This is to comply with our legal and regulatory obligations to keep records of our relationship, to resolve disputes or where it may be needed for future legal proceedings.</p>

  

</div><div role="tab" id="question-78721" class="border-top-coolgry-2">
